casebody.head_matter:
Richard Alan DAVIS, petitioner,
v.
Wendy KELLEY, Director, Arkansas Department of Correction.
No. 16-9721.
Supreme Court of the United States
Oct. 2, 2017.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Arkansas dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
